These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | lacrosse | golf | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pumpkin, cherry
1. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating pear is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pear | cherry | pumpkin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | collecting | video-games | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, folk, gospel
1. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | gospel | folk |

